This disc documents a 1987 Los Angeles concert by Ziggy Marley and the Melody Makers. 
 The English soundtrack is solid. There are no supplemental materials of any consequence, making it difficult to recommend this disc to anyone who is not already a reggae fan. 
Songs performed include "Tomorrow People," "Conscious Party," "Lord We a Come," "Time Will Tell" and a half-dozen others
